s-date=2017-10-27}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n|title1   = Nomad\n|length1  = 4:10\n|title2   = Freeze Me\n|length2  = 3:18\n|title3   = Caught Up\n|length3  = 4:30\n|title4   = Outrage! Is Now\n|length4  = 3:32\n|title5   = Never Swim Alone\n|length5  = 2:34\n|title6   = Moonlight\n|length6  = 3:10\n|title7   = Statues\n|length7  = 4:36\n|title8   = All I C Is U & Me\n|length8  = 3:00\n|title9   = Nvr 4evr\n|length9  = 3:50\n|title10  = Holy Books\n|length10 = 3:49\n|total_length = 36:29\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\n'''Death from Above'''\n*[[Jesse F. Keeler]] \u2013 bass guitar, synthesizer, keyboards, backing vocals\n*[[Sebastien Grainger]] \u2013 lead vocals, backing vocals, drums, percussion\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2017)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{album chart|BillboardCanada|20|artist=Death from Above 1979|accessdate=September 19, 2017}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DFA1979}}\n\n[[Category:2017 albums]]\n[[Category:Death from Above 1979 albums]]\n[[Category:Last Gang Records albums]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by Eric Valentine]]\n\n{{2010s-rock-album-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{more citations needed|date=August 2017}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Outrage! Is Now\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[Death from Above (band)|Death from Above]]\n| cover      = Outrage! Is Now.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = September 8, 2017\n| recorded   =\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = {{flatlist|\n*[[Hard rock]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.clashmusic.com/reviews/death-from-above-outrage-is-now|title=Death From Above - Outrage! Is Now|work=Clash Magazine|access-date=2017-10-06|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nowtoronto.com/music/album-reviews/death-from-above-settle-into-a-new-phase-on-outrage-is-now/|title=Death From Above settle into a new phase on Outrage! Is Now|date=2017-09-14|work=NOW Magazine|